OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCost of living: Food bank  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshame drives needy away -  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstudy                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Rules around food banks are driving    
OL,6, some people away from asking for help  
OL,7, because of the "sense of shame", new   
OL,8, research suggests.                     
OL,10,FCardiff University found that having to
OL,11,Fprove you are struggling to get a      
OL,12,Fvoucher for food creates more stigma.  
OL,14,FDr Andrew Williams said those in       
OL,15,Fclose-knit communities were more       
OL,16,Fworried about what people thought, and 
OL,17,Flikely to wait until "absolutely       
OL,18,Fdesperate".                            
OL,20,FIt comes as communities say they are   
OL,21,Fturning inwards to support each other. 
